d-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="枪花乐队的达夫·麦卡根和伊基·波普。图片来源：Tim Mosenfelder 和 FABRICE COFFRINI，来自 Getty" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/guns-n-roses">Guns N&#39; Roses</a>贝斯手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/duff-mckagan">Duff McKagan</a>透露了<a href="/artists/iggy-pop">Iggy Pop</a>在他青少年时期如何帮助他度过了一次“糟糕的蘑菇之旅”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/iggy-pop-cover-interview-2022-every-loser-3358737">伊基·波普 (Iggy Pop)：“我以为一旦我年满 65 岁，事情就会平静下来。但事实并非如此”</a></strong></li></ul><p>在出现在由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spandau-ballet" target="_blank" rel="noopener">斯潘道芭蕾舞团 (Spandau Ballet</a> ) 的加里·坎普 (Gary Kemp) 和受人尊敬的音乐家盖伊·普拉特 (Guy Pratt) 主持的<em>Rockonteurs 播客</em>中时，麦卡根讲述了他 14 岁时发生的事件以及这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-stooges">傀儡乐队</a>主唱如何帮助他摆脱困境。</p><p> “伊基波普让我度过了一次糟糕的蘑菇之旅。我去观看伊吉秀时蘑菇摄入过多，我以为我必须去医院，吓坏了，”马卡根告诉坎普和普拉特。</p><p>他继续说道：“我刚刚看完了《伊基》，只是迷幻剂太多了。但他让我失望了。我已经是伊基的忠实粉丝了，但后来我想，他对我来说意义更大。他是我人生的一个转折点。” </p><p><iframe title="Spotify 嵌入：S6E4：Duff McKagan" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/4mlto1YLLZBuvcIlO7JwRe?go=1&#038;sp_cid=72d8e289f4f4e5aaf9d8468db9286e1a&#038;utm_source=oembed&#038;utm_medium=desktop&#038;nd=1&#038;dlsi=c9161fb82e5d4375"></iframe></p><p>这位贝斯手对自己过去的药物滥用问题一直持开放态度，自 1994 年因急性酒精诱发的胰腺炎住院以来，已经清醒了 30 年。</p><p>他此前声称“我没有喝任何水。我刚刚喝了酒。我实际上已经 12 年没有喝过一杯水了。”<a href="/artists/van-halen">范海伦</a>前歌手萨米·哈加尔 (Sammy Hagar) 于 2023 年在后者的<em>摇滚公路旅行</em>电视节目中接受采访时说道。</p><p>去年在接受<a href="https://people.com/guns-n-roses-duff-mckagan-says-prior-to-getting-sober-wasnt-planning-on-living-past-30-exclusive-8399627#:~:text=A%20major%20shift%20in%20McKagan's,but%20that's%20just%20the%20truth." target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》</em></a>采访时，这位贝斯手表示，他的物质问题一开始是恐慌发作的拐杖，而他的健康问题迫使他面对自己的问题。</p><p> “我发现半瓶伏特加可以缓解惊恐发作。问题是，当你开始喝酒然后吸毒时，体内有太多的糖和酒精，而且没有睡眠，所以你会出现更多的惊恐发作。那么你猜怎么着？我越来越多地自行用药，”他说。</p><p>其他新闻方面，麦卡根最近发行了他的第三张录音室专辑“Lighthouse”，其中包括 Pop、他的枪与玫瑰乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slash">Slash</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alice-in-chains">Alice in Chains 的</a>Jerry Cantrell 等人。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guns-n-roses-iggy-pop-got-me-through-a-bad-mushroom-trip-3601948">枪与玫瑰乐队的帖子：“Iggy Pop 让我经历了一次糟糕的蘑菇之旅”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
