knot-artwork@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Mate-Feed-Kill-Repeat-Slipknot-artwork@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Mate-Feed-Kill-Repeat-Slipknot-artwork@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Mate-Feed-Kill-Repeat-Slipknot-artwork@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Mate-Feed-Kill-Repeat-Slipknot-artwork@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Mate-Feed-Kill-Repeat-Slipknot-artwork@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slipknot">活结乐队</a>的原主唱安德斯·科尔塞夫尼 (Anders Colsefni) 透露，重新录制的《Mate》喂养。杀。重复。&#39;未经他同意就被分享。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/corey-taylor-interview-cmf2-ptsd-slipknot-look-outside-your-window-3480518">科里·泰勒：“不要觉得自己很特别——我讨厌所有人！”</a></strong></li></ul><p> 1996 年演示磁带的新版本<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/original-slipknot-frontman-anders-colsefni-shares-new-version-of-mate-feed-kill-repeat-dedicated-to-eternal-brothers-joey-jordison-and-paul-gray-3601337">于昨天（3 月 14 日）在歌手的 YouTube 频道上分享</a>，并与去年随 Colsefni 巡演的新西兰乐队 KAOSIS 合作重新录制。</p><p>这位前主唱还透露，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknots-original-vocalist-to-perform-bands-demo-tape-in-full-on-tour-3457214">将演唱整首《Mate》。喂养。杀。</a>在现任主唱科<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/corey-taylor">里·泰勒</a>的祝福下<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknots-original-vocalist-to-perform-bands-demo-tape-in-full-on-tour-3457214">重复一遍</a>。不久之后，KAOSIS 在他们的祖国录制、混音并制作了修订版本，而 Colsefni 在爱荷华州录制了他的声音。</p><p>现在，视频上线几个小时后，该视频已被删除，歌手透露该视频是在未经他同意的情况下分享的。</p><p>我想就今天早些时候发布的 MFKR 与您进行联系。它是在未经我同意的情况下发布的，”他在 Instagram 上的一篇新帖子中说道。 “视频发布时，我还没有完成歌曲的音频混音。这个翻拍版并不是成品，我什至在发布之前都没有看过视频。”</p><p>他继续说道，并补充说他将取消即将上映的《伴侣》。喂养。杀。重复。&#39;巡演，而是将精力转向正确地重新录制。</p><p> “我希望你们相信我能正确地做到这一点，让你们和顽固的活结粉丝感到自豪。然后，我们将再次将这次巡演整合在一起，从它开始的地方开始，并扩展到您想要的范围。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4iZmhWOM4h/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 562.106,71.106 C56